well-rested and clear every day.

15
00:00:51,623 --> 00:00:54,313
Because they don't have
to dream at night. Why would they?

16
00:00:54,313 --> 00:00:57,913
You're an odd duck, Violet.
But I like you.

17
00:00:57,913 --> 00:01:02,445
I swear, 1929 is gonna be the most splendid 
year of my life. I'm gonna see the world.

18
